      "role": "user",
      "content": "medical professionals just want to keep me on more pills that make me feel like a zombie but dont even touch the pain. it's just a cycle of staying alive to suffer. i don't want more 'management' or more 'options' to cope. i just want the end of it. i feel like i'm just stuck in this loop of misery and there's no exit. sometimes i feel like there's a certain kindness in just letting go, you know? like, if the suffering is permanent, isn't ending it just a way to find some actual relief?",
